---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>About</h1>

      <p>
        I am a Business and Computer Science(BUCS) student at the University of British Columbia, with a strong interest in economics, especially macroeconomics, political economy, and institutional economics.
      </p>    

      <p>
        This website is where I publish short research essays and notes on public equities, macro trends, and business strategy. My research is mainly focused on the AI value chain, including both upstream infrastructure and downstream applications, as well as the long-term development of the energy sector, especially nuclear energy. I am also interested in how geopolitical risk creates investment opportunities, and I closely follow emerging markets outside mainland China.
      
      </p>
       <p>
		Outside research, sports are a major part of my life. I cycle, fence, swim, and practice taekwondo(1st Dan), and I also work as a soccer
		 referee. I follow ice hockey, baseball, Formula 1, and soccer, and I am a devoted supporter of Shanghai Shenhua.

      </p>
      <p>
        Nothing on this website constitutes investment advice. All views and articles are for research discussion and educational purposes only.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>